**Q:** "How much does the U.S Treasury have invested in Japanese Yen as of March 31, 2025? Convert the amount from dollars to actual Japanese Yen using the exchange rate for the same date."
**Strategy:** Single value lookup + currency-conversion MCP tool
```
1. grep -n "Japanese Yen\|Foreign Exchange\|Securities" /app/corpus/treasury_bulletin_2025_*.txt
2. Read the matched section, extract the dollar amount (check units — thousands? millions?)
3. Use the currency-conversion MCP tool:
